Sydney, Australia42 contributions
This Bridge "Dragons On"
With ample pedestrian footpaths either side of this iconic landmark, it gives access to the coast and city of Da Nang. Accommodating thousands of vehicles on a daily basis this bridges is never quiet, which gives it a character of its own.
This bridge in the evening provides opportunities to view Da Nang surrounded in neon lights. It also has great great eateries either side to dine in.
