Nice weekend event in Danang
Jan 2020 ‚Ä¢ Couples
Each weekend you can enjoy the Sin Tra Night market and some nice local music entertainment at the entrance of the Dragon bridge in Danang. We were there in December so it was probably busier than usual.

The Dragon is lightens up in various colors and around 9 pm there comes fire and water out of the dragon‚Äôs head. It not super spectacular, but great to experience.
It can be very busy so it‚Äôs good to arrive earlier to find a right stop to be able to take nice pictures and videos.
