Dragon Bridge event
Feb 2020 ‚Ä¢ Couples
Da dragon fires first fire than water for 5 mins every Saturday and Sunday at 9 pm.
They will close the street for that event and a lot of people come to see this.
Be ready to fight your way to the front for a better sight.
The dragon Bridge is good reachable from the son tra night Market where you can go eat before the event
