the dragon bridge has 10 minutes show on Saturdays and Sunday from 9pm.. it gets really crowded by locals and tourists.. if your in danang it wouldn't hurt to check it out.
you have some shows that take place by the riverside and also a huge market set up by the side of the bridge.. you got food custom key rings live portrait drawing and many more.. it's worth a walk.
